text: Jász-Nagykun-Szolnok is an administrative county in Hungary. The capital of Jász-Nagykun-Szolnok county is Szolnok. It is in the central part of the country. It borders with Bács-Kiskun, Békés, Borsod-Abaúj-Zemplén, Csongrád- Csanád, Hajdú-Bihar, Heves and Pest. In 2019, 370,007 people lived there. Its area is 5,582 km². Category:Counties of Hungary
title: Jász-Nagykun-Szolnok County
